Solar Flare Cosmic flux > threshold DFS + temporal gating 100 MHz 0.2 < 5 % ~0.5 Mbit/s

Switching logic:
The node monitors:

· Dust optical depth (from a sensor or MCD forecast).
· Raw QBER from recent sifted blocks.
· Cosmic‑ray flux (from a radiation monitor).

Pseudocode (conceptual):

```
initialize mode = CLEAR_SKY
rep_rate_physical = 1e9   # Hz
mu = 0.1
use_DFS = False

loop:
    OD = read_dust_optical_depth()
    qber_raw = estimate_QBER()
    cosmic = read_radiation_flux()

